  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Start the day with an excellent buffet breakfast, with hot and cold dishes to enjoy. On a Sunday there's a special brunch instead of the usual breakfast. Spoil yourself with dishes like salmon, rösti, and poached eggs, topped off with a glass of prosecco.</p>
<p>The hotel provides a complimentary daily packed lunch, so you'll be ready to head out and explore.</p>
<p>In the evening, tuck into a three-course menu with a choice of main. The hotel also has the cosy <strong>Arvenstübli</strong> à la carte restaurant which serves typical alpine dishes, and the <strong>Bärenstübe</strong> bar and lounge. There's a bar service on the terrace too, so you can sit and enjoy the beautiful Jungfrau views.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
